MID_支援_オボロ_タクミ_C: $t1$Wmオボロ|7$Wmタクミ|3$w0|$Wsタクミ|$WaOh, Oboro. Do you have a moment?$k\n$Wsオボロ|$WaLord Takumi...!\nDid you have some business with me?$k\n$Wsタクミ|$WaEarlier, I found a big\ndry-goods store in town.$k$pThere, I saw this piece of clothing...$k$pand for some reason, it made\nme remember how glad I was$k$pabout the clothes I received from\nyou for the Hoshidan ceremonies.$k$p$E笑,|I just wanted to express my\ngratitude again! Thank you.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,|N-Not at all...!\nI'm unworthy of your praise!$k$pAs your retainer, it is only natural\nthat I would select your clothing.$k$p$E通常,|If it were necessary,\nI'd even sew them myself!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E通常,|Really?\nI didn't know you could do that.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,|I can. I was the daughter of a family\nthat owned a dry-goods store, once.$k$pAlthough...\nthat's not the case anymore.$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E苦,|Oboro...$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E苦,|Ah! I'm sorry for mentioning\nsomething so gloomy!$k$p$E通常,|It's been quite a while since\nmy parents were killed,$k$pso I have no particular attachment\nto their old store now.$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E怒,|But in truth, you feel you want\nto work with clothing, don't you?$k$pDon't force yourself to pretend otherwise\njust because you're in front of your lord.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,|No, that's not the case!\nIt is my pleasure to serve you, my lord.$k$pThat's how I feel from\nthe bottom of my heart.$k$pThough I suppose it would be a lie\nto say that I have no interest in clothing...$k$p$E笑,|I mean, I keep hearing the\npeople around me say things like,$k$p“Lord Takumi is so well-dressed”$k$pJust having a reputation\nfor that is more than enough!$k$pThe reason you're so elegant-looking\nis thanks to me, after all!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E苦,|Hey, wait a minute...$k$pdoesn't that make it sound like you're\nsaying I'm not normally elegant?$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E苦,|N-No, that's not true! You're\nlike a big mass of elegance, my lord!$k$pIn fact, it's as if the personification\nof elegance itself had put on some clothes$k$pand started walking around in them!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E怒,汗|... when you go overboard\nwith your praise like that,$k$pit makes it sound even more contrived.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,|I am merely telling you the truth!\nI'm so happy to be able to refine$k$p$E通常,|your elegance even\nfurther, Lord Takumi!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E通常,汗|O-Oh... well, if you'd go\nas far as to say that, then...$k$ponce peace is upon our lands again,$k$p$E笑,|I'd like for you to make me some\nnew ceremonial clothing, Oboro.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E笑,|Yes, of course!\nPlease leave it to me!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$WaThen I'm counting on you.\nI expect great things from you.$k
MID_支援_オボロ_タクミ_Ｂ: $t1$Wmオボロ|7$Wmタクミ|3$w0|$Wsオボロ|$WaOh, there you are!\nLord Takumiii!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$WaOboro.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$WaSo, regarding what you said earlier\nabout me making you clothes once$k$ppeace comes to us again... how\nabout I use this type of clothing for it?$k\n$Wsタクミ|$WaYou've already thought of that?\nYou sure are in a hurry.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E笑,|That's because it was a direct\nrequest from you, my lord.$k$pAnd besides, thinking about\nwhat will come after the peace$k$pputs me in a brighter mood... if you\nwear it during the postwar ceremony,$k$pthe people of Hoshido will\nsurely take notice of it!$k$pI haven't thought anywhere\nnear hard enough about it yet!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E笑,|All right.\nShow it to me for a bit.$k$p............$k$pYes, I think this will work.$k$pThe fabric is nice to the touch and durable,\nand its glossiness is just right... I like it.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E通常,|Okay, then it's decided!\nI'll use this fabric.$k$pOh, I might want to ask you\nabout the color and such later, too.$k\n$Wsタクミ|$WaYeah, feel free to do that.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,|............$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E通常,|...?$k$pOboro...?\nWhy are you so silent all of a sudden?$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E苦,|Ah, no... um... it's nothing.$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E苦,|Did you by any chance\nremember your parents?$k$pDoing the same thing as they once did...\nit must be difficult for you.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,汗|Oh, no, that's not quite it.\nI did remember them, but...$k$pI was just wondering if they'd be happy$k$p$E笑,|to see me in charge of clothing\nthe Hoshidan royal family like this...$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E笑,|... they would. I'm sure they'd both\ntake pride in you being their daughter.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$WaThank you. But...\nheh heh, it's a strange feeling.$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E通常,|Huh? What is?$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E通常,|I mean, it's really unusual for you\nto be praising someone else like that.$k$pI don't think I've ever seen\nyou be this kind before!$k$pWow, it's as if the world's\ngoing to end tomorrow!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E怒,|Hey! I'm-$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E笑,|Hee hee hee, just kidding! I must\nthank you most kindly for your praise!$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wd$w0|$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E笑,|Geez...$k
MID_支援_オボロ_タクミ_Ａ: $t1$Wmオボロ|7$Wmタクミ|3$w0|$Wsタクミ|$WaOboro.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$WaLord Takumi?$k$pOh, are you here to\nask about your clothes?$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E怒,汗|H-How did you know?$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E笑,|It's my retainer's intuition, you see.\nI just had a hunch!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E笑,|Huh, that's pretty impressive.$k$pBut this time, I'm not going\nto discuss my clothes with you.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E通常,|Huh?\nThen... whose?$k\n$Wsタクミ|$WaI tried telling others about your talent\nfor finding the perfect clothes for others.$k$p$E通常,|Afterwards... the people who couldn't\nask you for help with choosing clothes$k$pcould simply come to me, and you'd\nget plenty of requests that way.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,|W-Would I really...?$k\n$Wsタクミ|$WaYeah. How about it?\nAre you willing to give it a try?$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E通常,|O-Of course.\nI'll do my best to cooperate with you!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E笑,|I see.\nI figured you would say that.$k$pThen I'll collect the necessary information\nand relay it to you, so look forward to it.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E笑,|Y-Yes, sir!$k$pBut... why would you\ntell everyone about me?$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E通常,|Oboro... you told me earlier you wished\nto work with something clothing-related,$k$pdidn't you? But you also told me your\ngreatest happiness was serving me.$k$pI thought that this way, you could\nkeep being my subordinate while$k$palso working with clothes in your\nspare time. The two can co-exist.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,|Lord Takumi...$k$pyou went through all that for my sake...\nI don't deserve such an honor...!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E怒,照汗|I-It's nothing special. It's only normal for\na lord to be considerate of his retainers.$k$pBesides, if you had said no, then my\ntalk about them co-existing would have-$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E笑,|No! I really want to do this!\nLord Takumi, thank you...$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E笑,|... yes.\nYou're welcome...$k\n$Wsオボロ|$WaEhehe...\nI'm so glad I became your retainer.$k$pHaving someone like you as my lord...\nis my greatest pride.$k
MID_支援_オボロ_タクミ_Ｓ: $t1$Wmオボロ|7$Wmタクミ|3$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E苦,|$w0|Um... Lord Takumi.$k\n$Wsタクミ|$WaOboro. What is it?\nYou don't seem too well.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$WaUm... about the people you were saying\ncould request clothing from me...$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E笑,|Oh, that. It seems like your\nfame has spread even further.$k$pI keep hearing people say,\n"me too, me too"... $k$pyou've been getting more\nand more requests lately.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa Umm, er... I'm very sorry, but\ncould you decline all the requests...?$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E苦,|What!?\nWh-Why!?$k$pEveryone was looking forward to having\ntheir clothes chosen by you!$k$pEven I...!$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,汗|That's... um...\nI... I'm...$k$puh... umm...$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E怒,汗|Oboro...?\nDid something happen...?$k\n$Wsオボロ|$WaI'm sorry... Lord Takumi.\nIt's all my fault!$k$pI was so happy to have a person\nlike you as my lord, and yet...$k$pafter being touched by your kindness...$k$pthe feelings I'd been trying to repress\nfor so long became unbearable...$k$pI don't think I can keep them hidden\nwhile staying by your side any longer...$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E怒,照|!\nAre you saying...$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,汗照|I... Lord Takumi...\nI've always...$k$ploved you...!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa............$k\n$Wsオボロ|$WaBut feelings like those are, by nature...\nones I should not have towards my lord.$k$pI mean... you're a prince.\nSomeone like me doesn't suit you at all.$k$pSo I'll resign,\nand leave your sight.$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E通常,|Then you're saying that\nyou'll leave your position$k$pas my retainer without\nfulfilling my request?$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E苦,|Yes... having someone like me by your\nside will only cause you trouble...$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E怒,|*sigh*...\nI must say, I'm very disappointed in you.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,汗|... I'm sorry...$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E苦,|That's not what I meant.$k$p... did you really think I never\nnoticed how you felt about me?$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E苦,|What...?$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E通常,|I always knew...\nthat you loved me.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,|!?$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E怒,照|And... I feel the same about you.\nI had planned on making you my bride.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,照|L-Lord Takumi...!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E通常,照|There's no need to get\nso worked up over this.$k$pThe fact that it's a relationship\nbetween a member of royalty$k$pand their subordinate doesn't matter.\nJust like how I'm the most important$k$pperson to you, you're the\nmost important one to me.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$WaTh-That's...\nthis is...$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E苦,照|Oh, come on. Dry your tears.$k$pThe reason why I ensured you'd be able\nto work with clothes... was because I$k$pwanted to support the person who would\nbecome my future wife, in my own way.$k$p$E笑,照|So, for the sake of a bright future\nbetween us... don't tell me that you'll leave my sight.$k$pleave my sight. Stay by me the\nway you've you've always done,$k$pand keep helping everyone\nfind the right clothing.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa*sob*... *sob*... Yes, yes...!\nOf course... I will...$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E通常,照|Good. Then what you said about\ncancelling all requests is void.$k$p... I'm sorry for making you wait so long.\nLet's stay together, always.$k$pAnd let's create a world of peace,\nand make your dream come true.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E笑,照|Yes... I'm so happy.\nI'll never leave your side, Lord Takumi.$k$pPlease... let me stay with you,\nalways, until death parts us!$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E笑,照|Yes, of course.$k$pI want you to be with me,\nfrom now until forever.$k
